Firſt, not uſurp it. They muſt ſtay for a lawfull calling: private men and women muſt onely act in their owne ſpheres and circuits, as Maſters over ſervants, and parents over children. Saint Pauls ſpirit was troubled in him at the idolatrie of the Athenians;



